        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 83–86. 83. Miridiba sinensis (Hope, 1842), lectotype, ♂ (BMNH). Habitus in dorsal view. 84– 86. M. pseudosinensis Keith, 2010, holotype, ♂ (DKC). 84. Habitus in dorsal view. 85. Parameres in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views. 86. Endophallus (everted) and temones in dorsal view. Scale bars: 83–84 = 5.0 mm; 85–86 = 1.0 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4770398/files/figure.png" .

