        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 12–14. Morphotype V “Sinensis”. 12–13. Male genitalia of M. sinensis (Hope, 1842), lectotype (BMNH). 12. Parameres in dorsal (A), ventral (B) and lateral (C) views. 13. Endophallus and temones in ventral view. 14. Female genitalia of M. dalatensis Frey, 1970, holotype (NHMB) in lateral view. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
